lead_paragraph: If you asked West Virginia coach Bob Huggins what he thought of his team's dominating performance on Tuesday night, you would expect him to be disappointed in their effort and how they were not ready for Big 12 competition.

headline.print_headline: No. 11 West Virginia Cruises Over Radford 84-57
